con:config.con:query: SELECT TOP 1 [OMAI_ID] ,OMAI.[OMAI_NR_LISTU] --,OMAO.[OMAO_CBO_OFER_ID] ,(SELECT [OFER_KOD] FROM [CBO].[SCH_OFERTY].[T_OFERTY] WHERE ([OFER_ID] = OMAO.[OMAO_CBO_OFER_ID])) as 'OFERTA_KOD' --,OMAI.[OMAI_DATA_WAZNOSCI_OD] --,OMAI.[OMAI_DATA_WAZNOSCI_DO] --,OMAI.[OMAI_CZY_WYKORZYSTANE] ,OMAI.[OMAI_IMIE] ,OMAI.[OMAI_NAZWISKO] ,OMAI.[OMAI_PESEL] FROM [CBM_FINO].[SCH_MAILING].[T_OFERTY_MAILINGOWE] AS OMAI INNER JOIN [CBM_FINO].[SCH_MAILING].[T_OFERTY_MAILINGOWE_OFERTY] AS OMAO ON OMAI.[OMAI_ID] = OMAO.[OMAO_OMAI_ID] WHERE ([OMAI_DATA_WAZNOSCI_DO] > GETDATE() AND [OMAI_DATA_WAZNOSCI_OD] < GETDATE()) AND [OMAI_CZY_WYKORZYSTANE] <> 1 AND OMAO.[OMAO_CBO_OFER_ID] = 1124 ORDER BY NEWID()
